==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Ґ''', '''ґ''' (''italics: Ґ, ґ'')


#The fifth letter of the Ukrainian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is '''ґе''' {{IPAchar|(gɛ)}} and it has the sound of /g/ - voiced velar plosive. It is preceded by [[г|Г]] and followed by [[д|Д]].

#The fifth letter of the Rusyn [[Cyrillic]] alphabet (both Lemko and Pannonian Rusyn orthography). Its name is '''ґе''' {{IPAchar|(gɛ)}} and it has the sound of /g/ - voiced velar plosive. It is preceded by [[г|Г]] and followed by [[д|Д]].

